Australia‚Äôs superannuation funds, worth $2.7 Tn, <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-08-03-2025-wn2-4-are-adjusting-investment-strategies" target="_blank">are adjusting investment strategies</a> amid global market challenges. Commonwealth Bank shares may drop 26% due to valuation concerns. Buyout firms Bain Capital and CC Capital increased bids for Insignia Financial. Cyclone Alfred threatens parts of Australia with heavy rain and flooding.
</p>
