        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/8-mar-2025.jpg" alt="Why does tech consistently outperform?" href="https://www.altdaily.co" />
             <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i>The magnificent 7 beats S&P 500 and the other 493.</i></p> 
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">

          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-size:20px; padding-right:5px;">‚Üí</span><strong>Robust cash generation:</strong> The Magnificent 7 typically generates significant free cash flow, which gives them the flexibility to invest in R&D, make strategic acquisitions, and reward shareholders through buybacks or dividends. This sets them apart in times of economic uncertainty.</p>

          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-size:20px; padding-right:5px;">‚Üí</span><strong>Scale & network effects:</strong> Tech firms benefit from network effects, where their platforms become more valuable as more users join. Combined with global distribution and vast user bases, this scale makes them attractive to advertisers, partners, and consumers.</p>

          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-size:20px; padding-right:5px;">‚Üí</span><strong>Relentless innovation and R&D:</strong> Whether AI chips, autonomous driving technology, or next-generation consumer devices, tech companies invest heavily in cutting-edge R&D.</p>

          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-size:20px; padding-right:5px;">‚Üí</span><strong>Visibility & liquidity: Given their massive market capitalizations, these companies are frequently included in major indices</strong> (like the S&P 500 and the NASDAQ). This index inclusion ensures liquidity and can increase prices as index funds and ETFs buy and rebalance.</p>


        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
